OL,3,CThree teenage girls admit killing a 75-
OL,4,Cyear-old man in a street attack
OL,6,FThree teenage girls have pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty at the Old Bailey to the
OL,8,Fmanslaughter of a 75-year-old man who
OL,9,Fdied following a street attack that
OL,10,Fwas filmed on a mobile phone.
OL,12,FFredi Rivero was set upon in
OL,13,FIslington, north London, on February
OL,14,F27 and died in hospital the next day.
OL,16,FThe victim, a Bolivian national, was
OL,17,Fnear a bus stop on Seven Sisters Road
OL,18,Fwhen the teenagers got off a bus and
OL,19,Fsurrounded him.
