OL,3,CThree teenage girls admit killing a 75-
OL,4,Cyear-old man in a street attack
OL,6,FThe girls, aged 15, 16 and 17, pushed,
OL,7,Fshoved, kicked and punched him, with
OL,8,Fone of them filming the incident on
OL,9,Fher phone and grabbing his glasses.
OL,11,FAs part of the police investigation,
OL,12,Fofficers recovered CCTV footage of the
OL,13,Fassault in which the oldest girl was
OL,14,Fseen to punch the victim in the head
OL,15,Fcausing him to fall backwards.
