OL,3,CThree teenage girls admit killing a 75-
OL,4,Cyear-old man in a street attack
OL,6,FPolice were called at 11.25pm to
OL,7,Freports of the disturbance and found
OL,8,FMr Rivero unconscious on the pavement
OL,9,Fwith a severe head injury and in
OL,10,Fcardiac arrest. He was taken to the
OL,11,FRoyal London Hospital where he later
OL,12,Fdied.
OL,14,FOn Thursday, the girls, who cannot be
OL,15,Fidentified because of their ages,
OL,16,Fappeared at the Old Bailey before
OL,17,FJudge Judy Khan KC.
OL,19,FThe girls, who appeared from custody
OL,20,Fby video link, pleaded guilty to
OL,21,Fmanslaughter.
