OL,3,CThree teenage girls admit killing a 75-
OL,4,Cyear-old man in a street attack
OL,6,FJudge Khan ordered reports and
OL,7,Fremanded the defendants into custody
OL,8,Fto be sentenced on September 5.
OL,9,FPreviously, police have said Mr Rivero
OL,10,Fwas a "much-loved father" whose family
OL,11,Fwere "devastated by his death".
OL,13,FMr Rivero's daughter, ex-wife and
OL,14,Fcousins also attended court for the
OL,15,Fhearing on Thursday.
